com.vmware.nsx_policy.infra.nvds_urt

Class NvdsUrtFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx_policy.infra.nvds_urt.NvdsUrtFactory

  • public class NvdsUrtFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    NvdsUrtFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx_policy.infra.nvds_urt package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
